The material plane is the [[plane|The Planes]] of existance that the world of [[Scorios]] exists on. It includes the planet, the sky, the stars, and their planets and is built upon the three Foundational Planes of [[Creation|The Plane of Creation]], [[Alteration|The Plane of Alteration]], and [[Destruction|The Plane of Destruction]]. All mortals are born, live, and die, on the material plane, and anything made of matter originates on this plane.